in:</span> <a href=\'https://wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/\' class=\'dashboard-news-plugin-link\'>Page Builder by SiteOrigin</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=siteorigin-panels&amp;_wpnonce=c1548071e7&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Page Builder by SiteOrigin\'>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>','no'),(129,'recently_activated','a:0:{}','yes');
